data.description: Here is your opportunity to own a spacious brick home with a huge back yard in Spencer.  This home has over 1900 square feet of living space with 3 large bedrooms, one full bath and a 3/4 bath with laundry room all on the main level!  There is also a great room between the house and the garage that ahs a gas fireplace and could be utilized in a variety of ways.  With a 2 car attached garage plus carport and 2 sheds in the back yard, there is plenty of storage for all of your toys. Don't miss your chance to make this home your own.
